original_title: Crosby, Stills, Nash & Young - Live in Wembley 1974
overview: 2-DVD set of Classic CSN&Y, at London's Wembley Stadium, on September 14, 1974. This pro-shot performance is excellent quality, considering its 30+ years vintage.
